<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEJaini199882-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEJaini199882_16-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFJaini1998">Jaini 1998</a>, p.&#160;82.</span>
